<p class="text-black mt-16 font-extrabold lg:text-5xl text-4xl tracking-tight items-center text-center">
    Launch CodeBlocks in minutes
</p>

<div>
    <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-slate-600 max-w-xl mx-auto items-center text-center">
        Deploy CodeBlocks on your own infrastructure, behind your own VPN, in your own VPC.
    </p>

<p class="text-3x1 lg:text-3xl mt-3 font-bold xl:text-7x1 text-slate-600 max-w-xl">
      AWS
<img alt="logo" class="max-h-6 " src="/amazontiny.jpg" />
     </p>

 <p class="text-black text-lg font-bold mt-4 text-slate-600">
      Use our AWS 1-click deploy with CloudFormation
  </p>
<p class="text-3x1 lg:text-3xl mt-3 font-bold xl:text-7x1 text-slate-600 max-w-xl">
      Docker
<img alt="logo" class="max-h-6 " src="/dockertiny.png" />
     </p>

 <p class="text-black text-lg font-bold mt-4 text-slate-600">
      Deploy CodeBlocks in less than 10 minutes as a Docker container or with Helm on Kubernetes
  </p>
<div class="bg-black text-white p-1 md:p-0 md:pt-1 md:pb-1 mt-4 mx-auto max-w-xs rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center text-center">
